" Customer Billing Management System"

MIS : 141508011
Name : Priyanka Devidas Sirsath

	Customer Billing System Project is a simple console application designed to demonstrate the practical use of C programming language and its features as wells as to generate an application which can be used in any departmental store, shops, cafes etc. for billing to the customer.
You can use this application to keep the records such as name, address, mobile number, paid amount, due amount, payment date etc. of your regular costumer. Moreover, if you have a new customer, you can add and view the account list at any time.
To run the project use command "touch file.txt" after the compilation.
